e-2024-11-30-at-00.40.03-1003x1024.jpeg 1003w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-00.40.03-294x300.jpeg 294w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-00.40.03-768x784.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-00.40.03-441x450.jpeg 441w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-11-30-at-00.40.03.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-032c6a3 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"032c6a3\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5734b96 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5734b96\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b1e106 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8b1e106\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Itinerary<\/h3>\n<p><b>Pick-Up and Scenic Drive:<br><\/b>Your adventure begins with a pick-up from your accommodation in Marrakech. Enjoy a scenic drive through the stunning Atlas Mountains, where you\u2019ll pass traditional Berber villages, terraced fields, and lush valleys.<\/p>\n<p><b>Arriving at the Berber Home:<br><\/b>Once you arrive, you\u2019ll be welcomed into a traditional Berber home where you\u2019ll learn to prepare authentic Moroccan dishes using fresh, local ingredients.<\/p>\n<p><b>Cooking Class:<br><\/b>Under the guidance of an experienced chef, you\u2019ll participate in the preparation of classic Moroccan dishes such as tagine, couscous, salads, and freshly baked Moroccan bread. You\u2019ll also learn about the use of unique spices that make Moroccan cuisine so flavorful.<\/p>\n<p><b>Enjoy the Meal:<br><\/b>After the cooking session, sit down to enjoy the meal you\u2019ve prepared, sharing it with your hosts and fellow participants in a warm and inviting atmosphere.<\/p>\n<p><b>Cultural Insights:<br><\/b>Throughout the class, you\u2019ll learn about the rich culinary traditions of Morocco and the Berber way of life, gaining valuable insights into their customs, ingredients, and cooking methods.<\/p>\n<p><b>Return to Marrakech:<br><\/b>After the cooking experience, you\u2019ll be driven back to Marrakech, with a full belly and new skills to take home.<\/p>\n<p><b>Highlights:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Learn to cook traditional Moroccan dishes in a Berber village.<\/p>\n<p>Experience the beauty of the Atlas Mountains and Berber culture.<\/p>\n<p>Cook with fresh, locally sourced ingredients and authentic spices.<\/p>\n<p>Enjoy a delicious meal that you\u2019ve prepared yourself.<\/p>\n<p>Gain insights into Moroccan culinary traditions from expert chefs.<\/p>\n<p>This cooking class in the Atlas Mountains is perfect for food lovers and those seeking to connect with local culture. It&#8217;s an unforgettable experience that combines delicious food, hands-on learning, and the stunning beauty of Morocco&#8217;s mountainous landscapes.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Cooking Class in the Atlas Mountains Immerse yourself in the heart of Moroccan culture with a unique cooking class set in the beautiful Atlas Mountains. This hands-on experience allows you to learn traditional Moroccan recipes and cooking techniques, all while surrounded by breathtaking mountain views and the peaceful atmosphere of Berber villages. Itinerary Pick-Up and [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11313,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11695","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11695","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11695"}],"version-history":[{"count":23,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11695\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12797,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11695\/revisions\/12797"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11313"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11695"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}